{"tid":2037371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［有圖］屯門娜娜用行動叫手足唔好放棄","createTime":"2020-05-27T02:56:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T05:32:27.000Z","uid":229185,"like":2,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4b5ff2466ad4dcd75d1256725fcd3fb4011bcbea","tid":2037371,"uid":229185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T02:56:48.000Z","msg":"上次我地都知道屯門娜娜係深黃到唔深黃啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［有圖］原來屯門娜娜係深黃<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2029554\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2029554</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/05/27/104251_3cbd817a9346603227e9a475e39c1ee5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F05%2F27%2F104251_3cbd817a9346603227e9a475e39c1ee5.jpg&h=0c88378f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次佢重cosplay 海賊王嘅娜美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wmmecwT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwmmecwT.jpg&h=7bc3acb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家有睇過海賊王都知道， 海賊王暗示著自由的心， 永不言敗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UB3weLN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUB3weLN.jpg&h=ac1679b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢次企係隻船，染左娜美隻紅色頭髮，係今日（27/5）影左張相比我地睇，暗示左好多野， 扮娜美比有好多信息我地，好撚有智慧！<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我睇返海賊王娜美語錄， 好多好有意思嘅信息比手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n娜娜係真係深黃嘅女神呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a69f6d87e0e84fbf7e8e77268d9aea0f19035546","tid":2037371,"uid":229185,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T02:58:47.000Z","msg":"公園隻戰線好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd7213ee20b16251deb80c986aba171806e32a15","tid":2037371,"uid":229185,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:00:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇人理"},{"pid":"d7f25d80500367c049b2ba02e219e5f8588182d5","tid":2037371,"uid":116910,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:01:14.000Z","msg":"可摸耳打格"},{"pid":"12d6c79e3e330d596e15cfe1fff90a6471d98695","tid":2037371,"uid":229185,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d7f25d80500367c049b2ba02e219e5f8588182d5","tid":2037371,"uid":116910,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:01:14.000Z","msg":"可摸耳打格"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:02:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你試過？"},{"pid":"3a517b8106bbb3c6cc7ae08a176a7025b0080b34","tid":2037371,"uid":274149,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a69f6d87e0e84fbf7e8e77268d9aea0f19035546","tid":2037371,"uid":229185,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T02:58:47.000Z","msg":"公園隻戰線好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.